In resident evil 4, special agent Leon  S.  Kennedy
is sent on a mission to rescue the U.S. President's
daughter who has been kidnapped. Finding his way to
a rural village in Europe,  he  faces  new  threats
that are a departure from the traditional lumbering
zombie enemies of the earlier  instalments  in  the
series.  Leon  battles   horrific   new   creatures
infested by a new  threat  called  Las  Plagas  and
faces off against an aggressive  group  of  enemies
including mind-controlled villagers that  are  tied
to Los Illuminados, the mysterious  cult  which  is
behind the abduction.

* Original Soundtrack
* Artbook
